name: Imagio Home Roanoke X-Back Stools, Set of 2, Rubbed Black

reviews.name: Imagio Home Roanoke X-Back Stools, Set of 2, Rubbed Black
reviews.reviewText: These stools are beautiful!! They look perfect by our island. Great quality, a little difficult to put together and needed some longer screws. The high backs make them comfortable and give them a grand look, yet they are still rustic enough to go with the rest of our decor due to the burnished black color. Shipped site to store for free, easy to pick up!
reviews.title: LOVE THESE!!

reviews.name: Imagio Home Roanoke X-Back Stools, Set of 2, Rubbed Black
reviews.reviewText:
First of all the picture does no justice to what these look in original. These chairs are easy to put together. In fact one needs to have patience to put such packaged items together and read the instructions first. All the parts were there and put together everything in a few. Another person would be helpful to hold it while putting leg supports together.

Very nice and elegant looking with a beautiful design and spacious feeling. Goes well with the table that requires these.
reviews.title: Elegant

reviews.name: Imagio Home Roanoke X-Back Stools, Set of 2, Rubbed Black
reviews.reviewText: They were a bit of a pain to put together but they look great! The seats are a generous size and they don't wobble. I got the counter height set. If you have some patience you can get them built in about half an hour for each one.
reviews.title: Excellent study chairs

reviews.name: Imagio Home Roanoke X-Back Stools, Set of 2, Rubbed Black
reviews.reviewText: I was surprised that we got 2 stools at this price! Other retailers charge more than that for one. The stool arrived well-packed with no missing parts. The instructions were hard to follow at first but I assembled them the next day with no problems. It came with an Allen wrench so I didn't need any additional tools. They are solid wood and very sturdy.
reviews.title: Sturdy and beautiful stools!
